(3055, 'nitroglycerin', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Nitroglycerin acts directly on vascular muscle. Marked symptomatic orthostatic hypotension has been reported when calcium channel blockers and oral controlled-release nitroglycerin were used in combination.', 'DailyMed'),
